<SYNC Start=64588><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=66966><P Class=ENCC>
Okay.
<SYNC Start=68797><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=108007><P Class=ENCC>
So how do you guys<br>like living together so far?
<SYNC Start=110237><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
